title: Party Wright Around The World S01E01 PDTV x264 TM mp4
description:
Party Wright Around The World follows Mark Wright as he travels the world looking for new surroundings and social groups, before throwing them the party of a lifetime.

Season 1, Episode 1
 Mark makes his way to Miami to create a very special birthday party. He stays with Hispanic party boys Alex and Miguel as he organises a party for birthday girl Joanna
